$ SQLcl: REPEAT
@ repeat

`repeat` executes a statement multiple times, similar to the shell command `→ Linux/shell/commands/watch`.

code {
SQL> select to_char(sysdate, 'hh24:mi:ss') from dual;
TO_CHAR(SYSDATE,'HH24:MI:SS')
________________________________
15:27:46

SQL> repeat 10 3
code }

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/SQLcl/commands
